title: São Paulo nº 157 - PRAIA GRANDE (3)!
text:

Série sobre o Estado de SÃO PAULO - O Estado onde NASCI e em que sempre VIVI - Região SUDESTE do BRASIL - nº 157! Series on the State of SÃO PAULO - The State where I WAS BORN and where I've always LIVED - The SOUTHEASTERN REGION OF BRAZIL - #157! PRAIA GRANDE (3) ! BIG BEACH (3) ! PRAIA GRANDE (BIG BEACH) is the first coastal city in the southern coast of the State of São Paulo! It's by the Atlantic Ocean! Santos, São Vicente and Guarujá are in the center! Praia Grande, Mongaguá, Itanhaém and Peruíbe are in the South! Bertioga, São Sebastião, Caraguatatuba and Ubatuba are in the north! I prefer the northern coast of the State of São Paulo, because everything is prettier and the cities / towns are smaller! This picture was taken when I went to PRAIA GRANDE back in november, 2011 because my mother, father, sister, brother-in-law and nephew were spending some vacation days there! I woke up early in the morning to go to the beach and get good views of a calmer place! SOME PICTURE DATA:
